profile:
Simply Blinds is a privately owned local business. Simply Blinds started in Collingwood, Ontario and now also services Toronto and the GTA, Orangeville & Shelburne area, Barrie and the Greater Sudbury area. We provide in-home consultations where you can see the products in your own home with your own decor and colour palette. We will make recommendations according to your needs and wants from your window coverings. We look forward to assisting you complete your home with window treatments!
Please contact us today to schedule a complimentary in-home consultation.
